    </div>

    <p>The three pillars of pediatric immune supplementation are vitamin C (immune cell function and antioxidant protection), zinc (immune cell development and communication), and vitamin D3 (immune gene regulation and respiratory defense). Elderberry extract provides additional anthocyanin-based antiviral support, though the pediatric evidence base is smaller. The most effective immune gummies for children combine all three core nutrients with elderberry for comprehensive, multi-pathway immune defense.</p>

    <div class="info-cards">
